{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "彩排日", "storyInfo": "長久以來盧西恩一直在驗證自己的臆想——劇團長或許已死而復生。藍卡塢拍賣會上具有劇團印記的劇本、進入劇組後發生的意外似乎都在告訴盧西恩，這次他或許找對了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g12_saluzzowinery", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一次參加本活動的朋友們，如果您期待的是炎國字畫或是薩爾貢秘寶，現在可以轉身離去了。", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“劇本拍賣”，作為藍卡塢最有特色的活動，這裡僅出售尚未成稿的劇本創意、大綱和相關版權。", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，不像傳統拍賣行會負責鑑定拍賣品的真假，我們並不保證拍賣品實際的價值——", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是否具有市場潛力，是否具有藝術價值，未來會成為叫好又叫座的作品被寫進藍卡塢的歷史還是賠錢貨……", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "均依賴各位自己去判斷。", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為保護拍賣品的智慧財產權，請各位收起終端，關閉錄音設備，接下來請容許我介紹今晚的第一件拍賣品——", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《杜邦夫人之死》，這個故事發生於哥倫比亞，講述了兩大家族在時代交替中的興衰愛恨，最低交易價——十萬金券。", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十萬！後面先生出價十萬……十五！感謝左手邊這位年輕美麗的小姐……還有其他來賓競價嗎？", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_auctionhammer"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十五萬一次……", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_auctionhammer", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十五萬兩次……", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "六十萬。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）格蕾塔女士！您今天是來砸場子的嗎！第一件拍賣品的開價這麼高，後面的氣氛只會越來越冷，其他拍賣品可怎麼辦……", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按規矩抬價太浪費時間，我只是報出了我心中它值得的價格。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花大價錢在劇本上賭博，是您的作風，但這樣不太划算啊……我聽說前段時間您投資製作的電影接二連三賠錢，現在手頭不寬裕吧？", "name": "拍賣師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還付得起你的仲介費，快落槌吧，老朋友。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在你這裡看上了一個天賦不錯的年輕人，正急著找他聊聊呢。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威士忌，不加冰，謝謝。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，也請你喝一杯吧？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的醫生規勸我不要飲酒。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽口音……你是薩爾貢人？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有趣，你這張冷峻憂鬱的臉，明明是標準的維多利亞人長相。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩爾貢語）我剛涉過薩爾貢的黃沙。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口音純正的維多利亞語）但確實生於維多利亞。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的語言切換得十分流暢，口音也挑不出毛病。不過除了這兩個國家，我還在你身上發現了其他文化的痕跡和習慣。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玻利瓦爾、敘拉古、萊塔尼亞、雷姆必拓……現在又來到藍卡塢。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——全泰拉最具娛樂性的移動城市，氣候宜人、陽光充足的拍攝地。你為什麼來到這裡？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "度假、遊學？還是像外面那些慕名而來，最終都擠在臨演市場的人們一樣，在尋找工作機會？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找一個人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#7", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漫長的時間裡，我循著他的影子，走過許多地方。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#7"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？什麼人？我認識所有在主城區和移動地塊上拍戲的劇組，說不定能幫上你的忙。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不勞費心。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，好吧……可惜……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你沒有別的事……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔·斯通，我的名字，藍卡塢電影製片人……在這一行的新聞裡出現次數還蠻多的。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來還以為你是哪裡的貴公子，或是來碰碰運氣的電影學院的學生，想邀請你加入我的劇組。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參加藍卡塢劇本拍賣會的人多少都會對藝術抱有熱情，再加上你的氣質很獨特……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾在維多利亞的一個小劇團擔任演員。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就說我的眼光不可能錯，你天生適合銀幕！", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過現在說這些也沒用，既然你有必須要做的事，看來今天我只能空手而歸了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能否看看劇本？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然！", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#4"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這份劇本原稿只是一個開始，我還會投入更多人力、資金、時間，讓它成為轟動影史的曠世佳作。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕你只扮演一個小角色，只在一幕戲裡登場，也能有精彩的成果。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你身上那些特殊的小問題也不用擔心。藍卡塢頒布了專門的感染者演員勞動保護條例，只要你支付了足夠的保險金——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_250_phantom_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫我盧西恩吧，格蕾塔女士。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會考慮你的提議。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "char_250_phantom_1#6"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須再次向你致歉，盧西恩。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你初次接觸電影，深思熟慮了很長時間才下定決心在演員合約上簽名。我本來應該像我承諾的那樣，讓你體會到拍攝的樂趣。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能想到，你在藍卡塢的第一場戲就親歷了如此可怕的事故……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你需要一點時間來調整自己的狀態，我很理解。我會讓謝莉更改你下一場戲的拍攝時間。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但要是你想直接毀約離開劇組，那恐怕行不通。移動地塊已經開出了短駁運輸車的調度範圍，直到租賃合約到期才會返航……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會離開。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不用更改日程。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用？這起事故造成的創傷性記憶很可能會阻礙你的表演，甚至影響你的生活。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台之上，意外於我並不陌生。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你習慣了舞台劇的演出方式，它的不確定性誠然比在鏡頭中表演更強，不過那終究是戲。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“戲”……或許吧。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "-500,0", "posto": "-500,0"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神秘優雅的生物不知何時又一次出現在盧西恩腳邊，她親暱地蹭了蹭菲林的小腿，對格蕾塔的出現視而不見。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，你確定不需要休息？你可以多享受一下Miss.Christine的陪伴。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她和我都在期待之後的故事。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對今天那件事的反應比我想像中鎮定太多……既然你如此篤定，若是我再有顧慮就顯得失禮了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們明天拍攝現場見。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Miss.Christine"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神秘優雅的生物梳理了一下自己的毛髮，她盯著盧西恩，若有所思的樣子。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩條尾巴在空中自由地擺動，搖曳出幾道模糊的黑影。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-500,0", "posto": "-400,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5, "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她飄浮起來繞著盧西恩的肩頭轉了一圈，好像是在觀察，又似乎是在品味。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#6$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終美麗的生物落在盧西恩的膝蓋上，提起一隻爪子輕輕抵在他的額前。盧西恩感到一陣恬適的暖意。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "酸澀。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空蕩的房間響起神秘的聲音，盧西恩輕易地就尋找到它的來源——他平靜地與一動未動的Miss.Christine對視。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他知道這是對方在他腦中投射的言語。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你習慣用沉默與偽裝避免麻煩，很少在無關緊要的時候開口。 ", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的情緒難以下嚥至此嗎，女士？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不討厭。就算不是偏愛的口味，我也樂於嘗試。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在想什麼？剛剛那條能說會道的小蛇不足以勾起你如此複雜的情緒。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在劇團生活的無數回憶之一。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長看出我的早悟，親自教導我如何使用武器。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天握住刀時的感受與那天一模一樣。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就能理解餘味中的辛辣與回甘從何而來了。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在劇團時體會的矛盾與掙扎，那些人類稱之為痛苦和悲劇的時刻，現在已經調理成氣味誘人的餐點，我很喜歡。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為殺死他之後，我仍在追尋他。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殘存的劇團信徒、偏僻村落的怪誕傳說，還有那枚張揚的印記……一路以來，我都在試圖驗證我冥冥中的臆想……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他或許，已經死而復生。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那條小蛇拍下的故事散發出一股令人上癮的古怪氣味。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#3$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你提醒我。翻看劇本時我已確認，書縫之中刻著劇團的雙生相印。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角色的偶然正是作者設定的必然，看似與劇團無關的格蕾塔女士成為了我們的領路人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此我仍無法確信。他留下的謎題真假參半，過去十年中我們已領教多次。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到今天道爾頓死於我的刀下，相似的感受牽動了過去的回憶……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他的邀請。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine，或許……我們來對了。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_MCcat_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵~", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}